"define the flags that correspond to the desired based build type, for "
"example, that ``-g`` flag that matches the Debug ``build_type`` in gcc-like "
"compilers."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../security/sanitizers.rst:359
msgid ""
"Using this approach, you can easily switch between different sanitizer "
"configurations and standard build types, preserving the package ID "
"differentiation based on the build type."
